020-03-15T18:07:34.000Z","msg":"戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvlYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=471dc737\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A</a><br />\n<br />\n中醫：腎虛百病叢生<br />\n<br />\n精由腎儲藏，而精既作用係用黎滋潤五臟六腑，所以丁得多會導致整個五臟六腑變差，就會出現好多症狀。<br />\n每射一次就傷身一次，包括做愛，夢遺（含精量唔多），而節制打Ｊ只不過係延遲你出症狀既時間／嚴重程度。<br />\n<br />\n每人體質唔同，症狀都唔同，以下為最常見：<br />\n早洩，變樣哀，猥瑣，臉色灰暗，自卑冇自信、腰痛<br />\n腦力下降，暗瘡，有口氣，脫髮、耳嗚、任何神經症<br />\n體臭，易怒，夜尿，表達能力差，社交恐懼症，雙眼無神，前列線炎<br />\n<br />\n戒丁必睇資料：<br />\n<br />\n戒為良藥<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.qiusuoo.com/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qiusuoo.com%2F2&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvlYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=c8fe046d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.qiusuoo.com/2</a>"},{"pid":"07bc137c2d0fbfe8a2424959829c83a7e32df136","tid":1927323,"uid":261812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dedb74b0e2ce2d24157af6858ed6598e9a7c132","tid":1927323,"uid":161404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:06:50.000Z","msg":"無論去幾多次按摩都冇用，都維持左幾年係咁，有咩解救方法？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T19:59:05.000Z","msg":"試下食鈣片十日 如果冇痛就係缺鈣 <br />\n冇分別就唔好再食<br />\n扁平足你由細到大喇 近幾年係轉左鞋款？"},{"pid":"9148b50d32d9bc78b88d85bc28807e23ef51d56f","tid":1927323,"uid":161404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07bc137c2d0fbfe8a2424959829c83a7e32df136","tid":1927323,"uid":261812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dedb74b0e2ce2d24157af6858ed6598e9a7c132","tid":1927323,"uid":161404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:06:50.000Z","msg":"無論去幾多次按摩都冇用，都維持左幾年係咁，有咩解救方法？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T19:59:05.000Z","msg":"試下食鈣片十日 如果冇痛就係缺鈣 <br />\n冇分別就唔好再食<br />\n扁平足你由細到大喇 近幾年係轉左鞋款？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:12:32.000Z","msg":"冇轉啊，都係著個D鞋"},{"pid":"55e003088